function create folder on signup:

curl -X GET "http://62.3.42.11:5002/init-store" \
-H "Authorization: Bearer mamad" \
  -H "storeId: asdfasdfasf"



post for upload image:
// add the domain of the vps on the response too

curl -X POST http://62.3.42.11:5002/upload/image \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad" \
  -F "storeId=storemdolh698v7th9n" \
  -F "file=@girl.jpg"


DELETE image:

curl -X DELETE "http://62.3.42.11:5002/delete/image" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"storeId": "storemdolh698v7th9n", "filename": "girl.png"}'


GET list images:

curl -X GET http://62.3.42.11:5002/images \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad" \
  -H "storeId: storemdolh698v7th9n"





//////////////json




POST update json file:

curl -X POST http://62.3.42.11:5002/json \
  -H "storeId: asdfasdfasf" \
  -H "filename: aboutlg.json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"key": "value", "example": true}'


Get the content of the json:

curl -X GET http://62.3.42.11:5002/json \
  -H "storeId: asdfasdfasf" \
  -H "filename: aboutlg.json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad"



GET list json files:

curl -X GET http://62.3.42.11:5002/list-json \
  -H "storeId: asdfasdfasf" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer mamad"